JOHN S. COX & SON
Aeronautical Supplies
TERRE HAUTE, IND.
Announcement
We take pleasure in presenting our first Aero-
nautical Supply Catalogue.
All the items therein we attempt to carry in
stock. Shipments are made to you the same day
we receive your order, if the article is in stock.
We contract for the entire output of a large
nitrate solvents manufacturer, and your attention is
especially directed to our prices on dope.
All our merchandise is "new production" and
we stand behind each item of our aeronautical de-
partment as we have in the automotive field for the
past twenty-one years.
Your satisfaction is assured and we solicit your
patronage.
JOHN S. COX & SON
